<section>
<h2>Problem Statement</h2>
<p>33% of users begin their journey online but end up calling for help. Our goal is to reduce this to under 30% by year-end by enhancing digital self-service.</p>
</section>
<section class="benefits">
<h2>Benefits of the AI Assistant</h2>
<ul>
<li>Reduces call volume and operational costs</li>
<li>Improves member satisfaction and trust</li>
<li>Provides 24/7 support with warm, empathetic responses</li>
<li>Guides users through complex tasks step-by-step</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section>
<h2>Sample Member Questions</h2>
<div class="accordion">
<div class="accordion-header">Where is my card?</div>
<div class="accordion-content">
<p>Hey there! I know waiting for a card can be a little stressful. Let’s check on that for you.<br/>
                Go to: <strong>Menu &gt; Cards &gt; Track Delivery</strong><br/>
                Most cards arrive within 5–7 business days. If it’s been longer, I can help you request a new one or connect you with support.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion">
<div class="accordion-header">How do I transfer money externally?</div>
<div class="accordion-content">
<p>Great question! Transferring money to another bank is easy once you're set up.<br/>
                Go to: <strong>Transfers &gt; External Accounts</strong><br/>
                Add the receiving bank’s routing and account number, verify the account, and then send money.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion">
<div class="accordion-header">What are your loan and credit card rates?</div>
<div class="accordion-content">
<p>Here’s a quick snapshot of our current rates:<br/>
                - Auto Loans: 4.75% APR<br/>
                - Credit Cards: 13.24% APR<br/>
                - Personal Loans: 4.99% APR<br/>
                - Mortgages: 5.875% APR</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion">
<div class="accordion-header">How do I find Zelle in Online Banking?</div>
<div class="accordion-content">
<p>To send money with Zelle:<br/>
                Go to: <strong>Pay &amp; Transfer &gt; Zelle®</strong><br/>
                Add your recipient’s email or mobile number, enter the amount, and confirm.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion">
<div class="accordion-header">Tell me more about the merger</div>
<div class="accordion-content">
<p>Our credit union is merging with DCU and First Tech Federal Credit Union.<br/>
                Benefits include expanded branch network, enhanced digital tools, and more financial products.<br/>
                The merger is expected to complete on January 1, 2026.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="gtm">
<h2>Go-To-Market Strategy</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong>Discovery:</strong> Identify top call drivers and digital drop-off points</li>
<li><strong>Prototyping:</strong> Build assistant flows for high-impact questions</li>
<li><strong>Testing:</strong> Launch internal pilot and gather feedback</li>
<li><strong>Launch:</strong> Deploy assistant in online banking and mobile app</li>
<li><strong>Optimization:</strong> Monitor usage, improve responses, and expand coverage</li>
</ol>
</section>
